Entering the "law" keyword into your Chrome omnibox gives you instant access to 1000s of pieces of authoritative (or as close to authoritative) Australian legislation for the Commonwealth, States and Territories.

Once you have the legislation you want, hit enter and the extension will redirect you to the most current version of the legislation on your platform of choice. You can choose between Government, Timebase or Austlii.
